-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                             ==== CHANGELOG ====

                               -- wxPTB --
							   Version 0.3.2
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

<<< 0.1.0 >>>
The first release!

<<< 0.2.0 >>>
+ Retry loading of the wxPTB again if it fails.
+ A config file for
  - maximum size of log-file
  - times to retry
  - waiting delay between retrys
+ info/about available with the option "--info"

<<< 0.3.0 >>>
+ unix/linux support
+ it is a real console application now
+ some micro modifications

<<< 0.3.1 >>>
+ modified thread handling
+ bugfixing

<<< 0.3.2 >>>
+ log messages with timestamp
+ option '-l' to display license information
+ more portable way to store log-, config- and sig-file
+ install routine for windows